beer.beer_description: Slicker than a can of grease and smoother than Danny Zuko, The Mechanic is here to service your thirst. Like a well tuned exhaust, the unmistakeable aromas of Citrus, Mandarin and pine steer you towards a radiating body of Peach, Apricot and Tropical fruit. Don’t be a dipstick, The Mechanics qu-oats include a full body tune-up that gives bitterness a brake for a pale ale you won’t tyre of!
